  "description": "<p>分类: <a href=\"http://cn.engadget.com/category/smartphones/\" rel=\"tag\">智能手机</a>, <a href=\"http://cn.engadget.com/category/tabletpcs/\" rel=\"tag\">平板电脑</a></p><div style=\"text-align: center;\"><a href=\"http://cn.engadget.com/2013/08/05/apple-to-restore-most-remaining-dev-center-services-this-week/\"><img src=\"http://www.blogcdn.com/cn.engadget.com/media/2013/08/wwdc2013-floor.jpg\" style=\"margin: 4px;\" /></a></div>\n\n<div><br />\n在过去的几周内苹果和其开发者社区的日子可不太好过，七月中旬的时候一位土耳其信息安全研究员<a href=\"http://cn.engadget.com/2013/07/26/apple-developer-center-back-online-following-hack/\">骇掉</a>了苹果的开发者中心网站，直到大约一周前它才刚刚<a href=\"http://cn.engadget.com/2013/07/29/ios-7-beta-4/\">结束了「停摆」</a>。但尽管如此网站的恢复工作还是进行得十分缓慢，不过好在苹果今天总算是放出了一些好消息。他们宣布会在本周内恢复大部份仍有问题的服务，其中包括了非常重要的注册、更新等。为了避免给开发者们造成困扰，苹果之前已经延长了现有帐户的有效期。接下来只要等他们把网站弄好，各位开发者就又可以<a href=\"http://cn.engadget.com/2013/06/10/ios-7-announced/\">重新开工</a>啦。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n经由：<a href=\"http://www.engadget.com/2013/08/05/apple-to-restore-most-remaining-dev-center-services-this-week/\">Engadget</a><br />\n引用来源：<a href=\"http://9to5mac.com/2013/08/05/apple-sends-out-developer-update-planning-to-restore-most-of-the-remaining-services-this-week/\" target=\"_blank\">9to5 Mac</a></div><p><h6 style=\"clear: both; padding: 8px 0 0 0; height: 2px; font-size: 1px; border: 0; margin: 0; padding: 0;\"></h6><a href=\"http://cn.engadget.com/2013/08/05/apple-to-restore-most-remaining-dev-center-services-this-week/\" rel=\"bookmark\" title=\"Permanent link to this entry\">此文章网址</a>&nbsp;|&nbsp;<a href=\"http://cn.engadget.com/forward/20687047/\" title=\"Send this entry to a friend via email\">转寄此文章</a>&nbsp;|&nbsp;<a href=\"http://cn.engadget.com/2013/08/05/apple-to-restore-most-remaining-dev-center-services-this-week/#comments\" title=\"View reader comments on this entry\">回应</a><hr size=\"1\" />", 
